10 SECTION 13. IC 36-7-4-1109.4, AS AMENDED BY P.L.223-2025,
11 SECTION 15, IS AMENDED TO READ AS FOLLOWS [EFFECTIVE
12 JULY 1, 2025 (RETROACTIVE)]: Sec. 1109.4. (a) This section does
13 not apply to the issuance of:
14 (1) a design release or a plan review under IC 22-15;
15 (2) a Class 2 permit according to the timeline set forth in
16 IC 36-2-7.5 IC 36-7-2.5 (after December 31, 2025); or
